<D>__{okee dokee, smokee.}
<A>__{margaret smiles and totters off.}
<C>__{paul}
<D>__{she's under a little strain right now.}
<A>__{ted looks down the hill at a small group of tv news vans, the reporters just now venturing out into the cold.}
<C>__{ted}
